}

findings.fix_suggestion:
latestAnswer()에도 _checkSequencer() 추가:
function latestAnswer() external view override returns (int256 answer) {
    _checkSequencer();
    (/* */, answer, /* */, /* */, /* */) = _calculateBaseToQuote();
}

